{"tid":1467764,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[集思廣益][不割席] 一齊檢討機場行動，同埋聽日點樣補救","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:12.000Z","uid":55886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88482892b3e020464a9932ac9c9b12d5537ce736","tid":1467764,"uid":55886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:45.000Z","msg":"前線就算戰略失當，和理非同冷氣軍師應該做既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫手一齊執手尾</span><br />\n今日好多鬼，好多卧底，好多捉鬼，甚至用左私刑等等<br />\n但係都已經經發生左，而家要做既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">補飛</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以後捉到鬼，仲會唔會綁起來打？</span><br />\n個人意見，明白現場所有人第一次捉到鬼一定慶過火屎，想將之前所有被捕既義士入晒佢地數<br />\n不過，而家情況有變，手足們要live with 場場活動都會有鬼呢個事實<br />\n或者，可能如果捉完，好幽雅咁記低佢，放佢走，係最好？<br />\n如果唔放，一路圍住佢幾個鐘，引晒班狗入黎拉人，為左隻鬼，輸幾個甚至更多既手足，又值唔值得？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日點好？</span><br />\n有手足話集體去機場道歉，有冇得諗？<br />\n呢Ｄ野可以交比純和理非做，前線手足可以休息一日，分工合作，留力紅土？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾，不割蓆，不分化，不互屌，一齊改善，一齊進步，一齊贏，一齊煲底除口罩</span></span>"},{"pid":"d3b51d1050eb47bd17bba349293779738de78fc9","tid":1467764,"uid":267639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"唔重要啦 唔好再開呢D POST<br />\n我地一定要目標一致 打倒邪惡港共政權<br />\n香港人加油！！！！！"},{"pid":"83b6e3a302e765fce5a9f2095bafc74b4ad404c0","tid":1467764,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VdzepBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdzepBi.jpg&h=624ac25d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBkATuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBkATuE.jpg&h=9007201a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6onyuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6onyuE.jpg&h=59d85c45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa7008f043b543ffec6e4e5c1730bc2dd84a01ad","tid":1467764,"uid":184070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n檢討<br />\n不割"},{"pid":"3776ae1efbb8e61f455a1e995dc6899ee0fd53c6","tid":1467764,"uid":290211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"集思廣益，入黎討論下開多條戰線啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[機場拆局] 對準政權 輿論Spin返去醫護集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}